title: Wellcome Trust aims to increase spend to £5 billion over next 5 years (Wellcome Trust) ...
text: ( Source : Wellcome Trust ) 21 October 2015 This marks another step forward for Wellcome, the world's second highest spending charitable foundation, which has invested £6 billion over the last ten years and £11 billion since it began in 1936.
